OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Alan Bates wrote to the government     
OL,6, criticising the speed of Post Office   
OL,7, scandal compensation payouts - just    
OL,8, days before he was made an offer.      
OL,10,FThe former sub-postmaster, whose story 
OL,11,Fsparked an ITV drama, said in a 22     
OL,12,FJanuary letter seen by BBC Two's       
OL,13,FNewsnight that the scheme needed a     
OL,14,F"radical boot up the backside".        
OL,16,FHe said he received a "cruel"          
OL,17,Fcompensation offer on Wednesday.       
OL,19,FBusiness Secretary Kemi Badenoch has   
OL,20,Fvowed to look into his complaint.      
